  <h1>8. Document Generation & Native Export Mechanics</h1>
  <p>
    The platform allows supervisors to export audit reports as PDF or Word files with a single click.
  </p>
  
  <h3>PDF Generation:</h3>
  <p>
    The app opens a clean print window and applies CSS print styles, hiding UI elements like sidebars, buttons, and settings so only the report content is printed or saved as a PDF.
  </p>

  <h3>Word Document Compilation:</h3>
  <p>
    The app generates a raw HTML string containing the call metadata, transcript, moments, and AI recommendations. It wraps this HTML in XML tags to format it for Microsoft Word:
  </p>
  <pre>
const htmlContent = `
  &lt;html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word'&gt;
    &lt;body&gt;...&lt;/body&gt;
  &lt;/html&gt;
`;
const blob = new Blob(['\ufeff' + htmlContent], { type: 'application/msword' });
  </pre>
  <p>
    Saving this file with a <code>.doc</code> extension allows Microsoft Word to parse and open it with correct formatting.
  </p>

